title: Inside Lara Bingle’s Harper’s Bazaar shoot
text: Inside Lara Bingle’s Harper’s Bazaar shoot 9:06 AM Victoria Nielsen IT’S BEEN a while since we’ve seen Lara Bingle in model mode. Now we can see inside her latest photo shoot. Gaga: ‘I feel f*cking old’ 8:50 AM Michele Manelis IN HER first acting role, Lady Gaga plays an elderly blood-guzzling countess. In an exclusive with news.com.au she says it’s a “dream come true”. Calvin: Break-up rumour is ‘bulls--t’ 8:43 AM Network Writer PICTURES of him leaving a seedy massage parlour have sent social media into overdrive with break-up rumours. Now Calvin Harris has fired back. ‘Grub’: Beau Ryan cops fresh backlash 8:03 AM Soraiya Fuda and staff writers BEAU Ryan has copped a fresh wave of criticism after posting a photo of his wife Kara on Facebook, amid suggestions of an affair. Mulligan reveals sex of first child 8:02 AM Staff Writers CAREY Mulligan and her husband Marcus Mumford welcomed their first child together recently, and the actress has finally spilled on the baby’s gender. ‘I’m the brains behind Beyonce’s success’ 7:25 AM Derrick Bryson Taylor and Network Writers SOMEONE very close to singer Beyonce is taking credit for her superstardom — and is even offering bootcamps for Queen Bey wannabes. Ex-Biggest Loser star’s stunning bikini pics 7:00 AM Charlotte Willis SHE’S been one of TBL’s biggest success stories, and Alison Braun has proved she’s looking fitter than ever seven years after appearing on the show. ‘It’s a very dangerous mix’ 6:50 AM Emily Moulton LAST night’s edition of Q&A dealt with the radicalisation of young Muslims. According to this man, our approach to the issue needs to change.
